"title": "8244: ethics, and grace",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8244",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Ethical conduct on the part of believers rests upon both the grace of God and human obedience.</p>\n<h2>People are unable to fulfil the law of God without divine grace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:14-Rom7:15\">ROM 7:14–7:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:46\">1KI 8:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:5\">PSA 51:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:6\">PSA 64:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:6\">ISA 53:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:22\">GAL 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8\">1JN 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Ethical conduct also depends on human obedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:16\">DEU 26:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12\">PHP 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:40\">DEU 4:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:17\">DEU 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:3\">1KI 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:38\">1KI 11:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13\">2KI 17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:23\">JER 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:17\">MAT 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:19\">ROM 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11\">1TI 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:7\">2PE 1:5–1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:14\">2PE 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>God assists believers' ethical endeavours</h2>\n<h3>He enlightens their minds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:1\">DEU 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:144\">PSA 119:144</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:23\">PRO 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:7\">ROM 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12-1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:12–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>He gives them his Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16\">GAL 5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15-John14:17\">JHN 14:15–14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3-Rom8:5\">ROM 8:3–8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9\">ROM 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:13\">ROM 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>He gives them spiritual resources</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3\">2PE 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:58\">1KI 8:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:13\">PSA 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5\">JHN 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:13\">1CO 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13\">EPH 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:13\">PHP 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:7\">2TI 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:18\">HEB 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:6\">JAS 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>God will bring believers to ethical perfection</h2>\n<h3>He will deliver them from the power of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24-Rom7:25\">ROM 7:24–7:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:8\">1CO 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">EPH 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:10\">COL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>He will make them like Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>He is preparing them for a righteous existence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:41-Matt13:43\">MAT 13:41–13:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">REV 21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">REV 22:15</a></p>",
